  "circuit": {
    "description": "RelayDT de-energised regime: both coil terminals tied together (in1=in2 via gnd) so I_coil=0A < dropOutI=0.02A, contact NO stays open (A1<->B1) and NC stays closed (A1<->C1). vTest=1V probes the contact loop through rLoadB and rLoadC.",
